></keycombo
></shortcut
> <guimenu
>Visualizza</guimenu
><guisubmenu
><inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata fileref="draw-circle.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
></inlinemediaobject
>Due colonne</guisubmenu
></menuchoice
></term>
    <listitem
><para
>Cambia la vista a tre pannelli predefinita in una a due pannelli. Per ulteriori dettagli, vedi <link linkend="view-change-columns"
>l'appendice</link
>.</para
></listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    
    <varlistentry>
    <term
><menuchoice
><shortcut
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap
>3</keycap
></keycombo
></shortcut
> <guimenu
>Visualizza</guimenu
><guisubmenu
><inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata fileref="draw-circle.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
></inlinemediaobject
>Tre colonne</guisubmenu
></menuchoice
></term>
